body: Hi @CarlaFernandez, can you try using runtime 11.0 with MLflow 1.28.0 and let me know if this issue persists?
I guess this issue is because of local installed spark client has different version with the remote connected cluster.

In the venv where I use databricks-connect I don't have pyspark installed. Furthermore, all my colleagues have the same problem, independently of their local machine setup.
